\nthey are the latest development of the\n\"Americanizing of London.\u201d\nBURIAL PERMITS\nMrs. Bridget Stevens, 218 Burnett\nstreet, age 73: asthma.\nJack Freeman, age 45, 711 Mason\nstreet; heart failure.\nMiss Eleanor Parks, the little\ndaughter of the late Judge Parks, who\nhas been at the Physicians and Sur\ngeons' hospital for an operation, has\nrecovered sufficiently to return to her\nhome.","height":"26320","width":"20364"}}
